org.opensourcedea.dea

Class ModelDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensourcedea.dea.ModelDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ModelDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class describes details of a DEA Model in terms of model type, and bounds. If more information need to be added to a model, this is the right place to do it.
    Author:
    Hubert Virtos
